1
00:00:58,021 --> 00:01:00,997
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:00,997 --> 00:01:02,967
=Episode 6=

3
00:01:02,967 --> 00:01:06,989
(Even a Rabbit Bites)

4
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:16,000
Dear.

5
00:01:20,319 --> 00:01:21,120
Step aside!

6
00:01:21,799 --> 00:01:23,519
What are you doing?

7
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:25,319
What am I doing?

8
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:29,400
An assassin appeared in the mansion.
I'm here for Zhaoxi's safety.

9
00:01:29,959 --> 00:01:31,280
But you're blocking me.

10
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:34,879
- Could there be...?
- There's no assassin.

11
00:01:35,239 --> 00:01:38,159
Instead, someone wants to use
the opportunity to settle personal scores.

12
00:01:38,159 --> 00:01:38,959
How dare you!

13
00:01:40,159 --> 00:01:42,480
Is this how your master
taught you to slander others?

14
00:01:43,799 --> 00:01:46,280
You claim there's no assassin
in this courtyard.

15
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,120
Then what is this?

16
00:01:58,840 --> 00:01:59,640
Seize her.

17
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:17,960
(Vast Mind, Eternal Will)
An assassin broke in tonight.

18
00:02:18,599 --> 00:02:21,479
Zhaoxi, for your safety,
please cooperate with the search.

19
00:02:40,319 --> 00:02:41,120
Zhaoxi.

20
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:47,639
Sorry.

21
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:03,199
Chaosheng, why are you
pressing me so hard?

22
00:03:04,039 --> 00:03:08,240
Just because I never compete,
you think you can push me around?

23
00:03:11,439 --> 00:03:12,080
No.

24
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,439
If it's about safety,

25
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:15,759
where were you when bandits attacked me?

26
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:20,280
Yes. You didn't search for me.
You just set up a memorial hall at home.

27
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,360
Such brotherhood.

28
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:25,439
How am I supposed to repay you?

29
00:03:26,479 --> 00:03:28,960
Alright, it's just hearsay.

30
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:33,919
I was sleeping with my wife just now.

31
00:03:34,479 --> 00:03:35,879
You know full well I'm injured.

32
00:03:36,879 --> 00:03:39,360
Yet you barged into my room
at this hour with such an excuse.

33
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,879
What exactly do you want?

34
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:46,479
Chaosheng.

35
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:49,159
I won't see you out.

36
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,040
Why did you...?

37
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,680
You didn't need to do that just now.

38
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:37,759
You could have just made up
an excuse to send him away.

39
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,120
Let me apply the medicine.

40
00:04:53,319 --> 00:04:55,120
You shouldn't have confronted him.

41
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:59,199
Zhaoxi has a gentle nature.

42
00:05:00,079 --> 00:05:02,199
He doesn't argue with others.

43
00:05:05,399 --> 00:05:06,199
Luckily,

44
00:05:07,839 --> 00:05:09,000
he didn't suspect anything.

45
00:05:19,279 --> 00:05:22,040
What else could I do?
Even a rabbit bites.

46
00:05:23,319 --> 00:05:25,240
A man, no matter how gentle his nature,

47
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:27,680
should protect his own wife.

48
00:05:31,959 --> 00:05:34,079
So this is how your beloved husband

49
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:36,199
protects you?

50
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:46,519
It's late. Get some sleep.

51
00:05:52,079 --> 00:05:55,759
Stay here tonight.
I'm afraid they might come back.

52
00:06:12,896 --> 00:06:15,104
(Earth)

53
00:06:20,319 --> 00:06:21,199
Master.

54
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:25,279
I think you know why I summoned you.

55
00:06:25,959 --> 00:06:26,759
Yes.

56
00:06:28,279 --> 00:06:31,680
These past two years,
I've had you by Chaosheng's side.

57
00:06:32,519 --> 00:06:33,879
(Zhe Zhu, Earth Unit, Xuanji Pavilion)
You remember

58
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,120
how to do a task, right?

59
00:06:36,519 --> 00:06:37,319
Yes.

60
00:06:40,544 --> 00:06:41,800
(Earth)

61
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:45,439
Here is the task and your identity.

62
00:06:45,839 --> 00:06:48,720
It's only an Earth-level task,
but it has wide-reaching implications.

63
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:52,839
Your painting skills
are among the best in the Earth Unit.

64
00:06:53,439 --> 00:06:55,879
So you'll complete this task.

65
00:06:56,079 --> 00:06:57,480
I will not fail the task.

66
00:06:59,519 --> 00:07:00,319
Go.

67
00:07:08,736 --> 00:07:10,720
(Tianfeng Pavilion, Gu Mansion)

68
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,480
Who does he think he is?

69
00:07:13,399 --> 00:07:15,000
Showing me such disrespect!

70
00:07:15,639 --> 00:07:16,720
Without his mother,

71
00:07:17,399 --> 00:07:19,360
Father wouldn't give
such an absurd order!

72
00:07:21,199 --> 00:07:22,000
Where is Zhe Zhu?

73
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:24,600
Miss Zhe Zhu went to the back mountain.

74
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,439
There's likely a new task for her.

75
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:29,600
Master.

76
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,160
You may leave.

77
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,360
Yes.

78
00:07:43,319 --> 00:07:44,319
There's a new task?

79
00:07:44,439 --> 00:07:45,240
Yes.

80
00:07:45,959 --> 00:07:48,319
The Pavilion Master ordered me
to pack and depart tomorrow.

81
00:07:48,639 --> 00:07:50,720
Although this task may be dangerous,

82
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:53,319
the reward will be huge.

83
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:56,279
Then I'll be of great help to you.

84
00:07:58,959 --> 00:07:59,920
It's dangerous?

85
00:08:01,079 --> 00:08:03,959
Don't worry, Master.
I will complete the task successfully.

86
00:08:06,319 --> 00:08:07,120
Let me see.

87
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:13,839
It's just the two of us here. Relax.

88
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:17,639
No one else will know.

89
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:21,319
Master, this task
is from the Xuanji Pavilion...

90
00:08:21,319 --> 00:08:22,800
Who is your real master?

91
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:25,360
I haven't forgotten.

92
00:08:25,839 --> 00:08:27,839
Ever since I became your death guard,

93
00:08:27,959 --> 00:08:29,519
my life has belonged to you.

94
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:32,279
My accepting this task
from the Xuanji Pavilion

95
00:08:32,519 --> 00:08:35,279
is also in hopes of
better assisting you in the future.

96
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:39,480
If that's the case,

97
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:42,600
give it to me.

98
00:08:58,336 --> 00:08:59,746
(Prince Consort seeks painters.)

99
00:08:59,746 --> 00:09:01,568
(Blindness for those
who fail. Investigate.)

100
00:09:04,399 --> 00:09:05,840
I remember in the Xuanji Pavilion,

101
00:09:06,519 --> 00:09:08,559
the only first-class painters
are you and Yuluo.

102
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:09,799
Yes.

103
00:09:11,399 --> 00:09:15,519
Go tell them you can't take this task.

104
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,799
But... Master.

105
00:09:17,799 --> 00:09:20,720
You know this task is dangerous.

106
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:23,279
How could I let you risk your life?

107
00:09:29,559 --> 00:09:30,360
I don't need

108
00:09:31,679 --> 00:09:32,960
to teach you what to do, do I?

109
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:20,399
You're awake.

110
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:43,759
Seems I came at a bad time.
I'll wait in the courtyard.

111
00:10:43,759 --> 00:10:44,480
No rush.

112
00:10:58,360 --> 00:11:02,200
Are you just using me
and then throwing me away?

113
00:11:22,519 --> 00:11:24,320
Who said I'd throw you away?

114
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:27,159
Honey, what more do you want?

115
00:12:18,159 --> 00:12:19,200
Is this enough?

116
00:12:28,160 --> 00:12:30,581
(Fufeng Pavilion)

117
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:40,639
You came so soon.

118
00:12:40,919 --> 00:12:41,799
Take your time.

119
00:12:41,799 --> 00:12:42,759
I'm not in a hurry.

120
00:12:52,039 --> 00:12:55,120
Didn't we agree days ago
to take your and Zhaoxi's measurements?

121
00:12:55,639 --> 00:12:57,039
So I've brought them with me.

122
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:58,799
Go ahead.

123
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:00,159
Yes.

124
00:13:13,919 --> 00:13:17,320
Wanniang, this is the lady
needing measurements today.

125
00:13:19,799 --> 00:13:21,279
So you're Leng Yan's...

126
00:13:21,879 --> 00:13:25,600
Yes. Though I often stayed
by Leng Yan's side,

127
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:28,519
I knew little of his business.

128
00:13:29,159 --> 00:13:31,159
But half a month before his death,

129
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:33,919
a man in black did come to hire him.

130
00:13:44,159 --> 00:13:44,960
Who's there?

131
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:53,080
(About ten days ago,)

132
00:13:53,840 --> 00:13:57,320
(he left some silver
at night as a deposit.)

133
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:59,159
I think I heard him say...

134
00:14:02,519 --> 00:14:04,759
Outside the city at Hai hour.

135
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:07,600
You'll get the rest when the job's done.

136
00:14:08,039 --> 00:14:08,840
Alright.

137
00:14:10,879 --> 00:14:11,720
(At Hai hour.)

138
00:14:12,679 --> 00:14:14,000
(And outside the city?)

139
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:16,879
I noticed a faint, unique fragrance.

140
00:14:17,360 --> 00:14:19,919
It wasn't any common scent.

141
00:14:20,039 --> 00:14:22,559
Likely custom-blended for nobility.

142
00:14:22,759 --> 00:14:26,519
As a perfume connoisseur,
I remember it clearly.

143
00:14:27,039 --> 00:14:31,120
Later, when Miss Gu had me
listen to Master Chaosheng's voice,

144
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:35,240
(I realized his scent
matched that night's exactly.)

145
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:39,200
Chaosheng made his fragrance specially.

146
00:14:39,279 --> 00:14:40,519
He's the only user.

147
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:44,799
Many in the mansion know this.
You can verify it, Yuluo.

148
00:14:45,559 --> 00:14:48,200
Chaosheng is involved
in Zhaoxi's incident.

149
00:14:48,639 --> 00:14:51,480
I just wonder
how Father will punish him.

150
00:14:54,440 --> 00:14:55,240
At Hai hour?

151
00:14:57,879 --> 00:15:00,360
Did Leng Yan ever act ahead of schedule?

152
00:15:00,639 --> 00:15:02,120
Moving early risked complications.

153
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:05,279
He never changed clients' set times.

154
00:15:05,480 --> 00:15:08,480
He called it an unbreakable rule.

155
00:15:09,360 --> 00:15:12,440
Did Leng Yan mention
anything when he returned?

156
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:15,080
I never participated in his business.

157
00:15:15,360 --> 00:15:16,679
Nor did I ask.

158
00:15:17,200 --> 00:15:19,919
But I remember
he returned very late that day.

159
00:15:20,159 --> 00:15:22,360
He was muttering angrily,

160
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:24,039
"I can't get my pay now."

161
00:15:25,480 --> 00:15:27,440
His task failed, didn't it?

162
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:31,159
Didn't Master Zhaoxi return safely?

163
00:15:34,200 --> 00:15:35,120
Was he injured?

164
00:15:35,960 --> 00:15:36,759
No.

165
00:15:37,200 --> 00:15:39,039
The deposit silver from that day.

166
00:15:40,039 --> 00:15:42,679
Was it taken away
when Leng Yan was killed?

167
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:44,399
No.

168
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:48,679
But when I fetched my clothes later,

169
00:15:48,799 --> 00:15:51,360
I found another bag of silver
hidden behind the door.

170
00:15:59,080 --> 00:16:01,600
There must be someone else
behind Zhaoxi's assassination.

171
00:16:06,600 --> 00:16:10,320
Since Zhaoxi doesn't know martial arts,
the killer returning unhurt is possible.

172
00:16:11,360 --> 00:16:15,039
Guards said the assassination
happened at Xu hour.

173
00:16:15,679 --> 00:16:16,759
If true,

174
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:20,519
when Leng Yan arrived,
Zhaoxi might've already been...

175
00:16:21,720 --> 00:16:25,200
Besides, if Chaosheng hired
and then killed the killer,

176
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:29,279
he'd take away the silver
to clear suspicion.

177
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:32,399
But he secretly delivered
the second payment.

178
00:16:32,799 --> 00:16:36,080
Meaning he likely
didn't know Leng Yan failed.

179
00:16:36,200 --> 00:16:37,039
The Xu hour.

180
00:16:38,639 --> 00:16:40,639
Interesting. So...

181
00:16:40,840 --> 00:16:43,919
Chaosheng hired the killer,
but someone struck first.

182
00:16:44,120 --> 00:16:45,559
He was unaware of that.

183
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:50,720
Then who appeared at Xu hour that day?

184
00:16:51,879 --> 00:16:54,679
Or perhaps Chaosheng
staged this whole play.

185
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:55,879
What do you think?

186
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:58,240
Maybe it was me.

187
00:16:58,559 --> 00:17:00,360
How will you handle this, Yuluo?

188
00:17:01,159 --> 00:17:02,720
Since Zhaoxi returned safely,

189
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:05,359
this is just a family matter.

190
00:17:07,240 --> 00:17:09,559
We're doing
your wedding gown fitting today.

191
00:17:09,880 --> 00:17:10,680
Wanniang.

192
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:12,119
Don't worry.

193
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:13,240
No rush.

194
00:17:14,799 --> 00:17:16,200
I appreciate

195
00:17:16,680 --> 00:17:18,559
your kindness.

196
00:17:19,119 --> 00:17:23,319
But I'm more curious
about how you two met

197
00:17:24,200 --> 00:17:27,079
and how you learned the details.

198
00:17:30,079 --> 00:17:31,480
How have you been lately, Master?

199
00:17:31,640 --> 00:17:33,000
Did they notice anything?

200
00:17:33,559 --> 00:17:35,480
I wanted to go to you
at the last lantern event.

201
00:17:35,519 --> 00:17:37,440
But that female guard
kept shadowing you.

202
00:17:39,319 --> 00:17:40,519
Are you sure

203
00:17:41,079 --> 00:17:43,839
Gu Zhaoxi has no martial arts skills?

204
00:17:44,640 --> 00:17:47,920
Yes. He's been frail since childhood
and couldn't practice martial arts.

205
00:17:48,559 --> 00:17:50,039
Why do you ask?

206
00:17:51,519 --> 00:17:53,279
If that's true,

207
00:17:53,640 --> 00:17:56,759
why did Gu Chaosheng
test my martial skills?

208
00:18:14,960 --> 00:18:18,000
It seems those two aren't allies.

209
00:18:24,032 --> 00:18:27,306
(Gu Chaosheng hired
assassin Leng Yan to kill Gu Zhaoxi.)

210
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:29,799
Leng Yan.

211
00:18:30,519 --> 00:18:31,319
Yes.

212
00:18:31,599 --> 00:18:33,640
Gu Chaosheng is truly ruthless.

213
00:18:33,720 --> 00:18:35,559
He hired an assassin
to kill his own brother.

214
00:18:36,559 --> 00:18:39,359
So Gu Zhaoxi was truly murdered by him?

215
00:18:40,160 --> 00:18:41,960
And the one you encountered was also...?

216
00:18:43,920 --> 00:18:44,960
Turns out

217
00:18:45,359 --> 00:18:46,160
blood isn't thicker

218
00:18:47,160 --> 00:18:48,400
than money and power.

219
00:18:49,440 --> 00:18:50,240
Master.

220
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:53,640
It's not as simple as it looks.

221
00:18:53,920 --> 00:18:55,599
Return to the palace and investigate

222
00:18:55,960 --> 00:18:58,440
what that person has been doing lately.

223
00:18:58,519 --> 00:18:59,039
Yes.

224
00:18:59,039 --> 00:19:03,640
Gu Yuluo has a blade wound on her back,
likely from the past month.

225
00:19:04,519 --> 00:19:07,039
Investigate it carefully.

226
00:19:07,400 --> 00:19:08,200
Yes.

227
00:19:09,480 --> 00:19:11,079
Master, do you suspect it was her?

228
00:19:11,079 --> 00:19:11,839
Dear.

229
00:19:49,925 --> 00:19:54,988
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

230
00:19:55,525 --> 00:20:00,846
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

231
00:20:01,413 --> 00:20:08,041
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

232
00:20:08,041 --> 00:20:12,805
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

233
00:20:12,805 --> 00:20:15,141
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

234
00:20:15,141 --> 00:20:21,841
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

235
00:20:21,841 --> 00:20:28,613
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

236
00:20:28,613 --> 00:20:35,749
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

237
00:20:35,749 --> 00:20:40,133
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

238
00:20:40,133 --> 00:20:42,757
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

239
00:20:42,757 --> 00:20:49,391
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

240
00:20:49,391 --> 00:20:55,941
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

241
00:20:55,941 --> 00:21:03,065
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

242
00:21:03,155 --> 00:21:07,525
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

243
00:21:07,525 --> 00:21:10,233
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

244
00:21:10,233 --> 00:21:16,133
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

245
00:21:16,773 --> 00:21:22,761
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

